<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_07_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_07_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">              
              0.21과
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>4</span>
              </div>
              의 크기를 비교하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 class="title" lang="y">0.21을 분수로 나타내고, 두 분수를 통분해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <div class="question_box gap_12">
              <div class="bracket lg">
                <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                <span>0.21</span>
                <span class="comma">,</span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>4</span>
                </div>
                <span class="bracket-r"></span>
              </div>
              <img src="../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg" class="obj_arrow" alt="" />
              <div class="bracket">
                <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="21"></math-field></div>
                  <span>100</span>
                </div>
                <span class="comma">,</span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>4</span>
                </div>
                <span class="bracket-r"></span>
              </div>
              <img src="../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg" class="obj_arrow" alt="" />
              <div class="bracket">
                <span class="bracket-l"></span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="21"></math-field></div>
                  <span>100</span>
                </div>
                <span class="comma">,</span>
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="25"></math-field></div>
                  <span>100</span>
                </div>
                <span class="bracket-r"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <div lang="y">
                    0.21은 소수 두 자리 수이므로 분모가 100인 분수로 나타내면 0.21=
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>21</span>
                      <span>100</span>
                    </div>
                    입니다.
                  </div>

                  <div lang="y">
                    4×25=100이므로 분모와 분자에 각각 25를 곱하면
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span>4</span>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>1×25</span>
                      <span>4×25</span>
                    </div>
                    =
                    <div class="fraction_box">
                      <span>25</span>
                      <span>100</span>
                    </div>
                    입니다.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 class="title" lang="y">
            두 수의 크기를 비교하여 <span class="circle_blank"></span> 안에 <img src="./../../common_contents/common/img/icon_arrow_right.svg" alt="크다" /><span class="ml-14">,</span> <img src="./../../common_contents/common/img/icon_equal.svg" alt="같다" /><span class="ml-14">,</span>
            <img src="./../../common_contents/common/img/icon_arrow_left.svg" alt="작다" />
            중 알맞은 것을 고르세요.
          </h3>
          <div class="flex justify_center">
            <div class="question_box">
              <span>0.21</span>
              <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                <select class="custom_dropdown math_symbol" data-answer-single="<">
                  <option></option>
                  <option value=">">></option>
                  <option value="=">=</option>
                  <option value="<"><</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>4</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>21</span>
                    <span>100</span>
                  </div>
                  &lt;
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>25</span>
                    <span>100</span>
                  </div>
                  ➔ 0.21 &lt;
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span>1</span>
                    <span>4</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
